{"tid":2309460,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2020泰國「最美變性人」MISS TIFFANY出爐！　三年前亞軍再戰封后","createTime":"2020-12-02T14:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T14:38:42.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a3933ed6599bbedb9225a52f5ee5e256b5b36ca5","tid":2309460,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T14:24:09.000Z","msg":"泰國一年一度的變性人選美大賽「蒂芬妮環球小姐 MISS TIFFANY 」日前在芭達雅舉行，由20歲佳麗Nong Rock奪下后冠。自29位佳麗中脫穎而出的Nong Rock，膚白貌美也相當有氣質，她過去曾在同一個比賽中獲得亞軍，三年後重新參賽，終於封后。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5310/d5310045.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5310%2Fd5310045.jpg&h=880e7be7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲2020「蒂芬妮環球小姐」由三年前亞軍Nong Rock奪下后冠。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／Miss Tiffany's Universe）<br />\n<br />\nNong Rock（本名：Kwanlada Rungrojampa）三年前也曾參加「蒂芬妮環球小姐」，當時獲得亞軍。今年20歲的她，終於打敗其他28名佳麗，成功戴上后冠。Nong Rock就讀泰國戲劇藝術學院，不僅外型佼好，落落大方的笑容更是氣質過人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5310/d5310047.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5310%2Fd5310047.jpg&h=ca2b7c9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲2020「蒂芬妮環球小姐」冠軍Nong Rock淡妝一樣美麗。（圖／翻攝自IG／rock_kwanlada）<br />\n<br />\nNong Rock也是泰國第23位「蒂芬妮環球小姐」，該選美比賽每年都吸引無數佳麗參加，她們個個環肥燕瘦，各自擁有不同的美麗，唯一的共通點就是「她」們都具有跨性別的身份。雖然生下時是男兒身，但各個都出落得美麗大方，比女人更像女人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5310/d5310046.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5310%2Fd5310046.jpg&h=06817c04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲2020「蒂芬妮環球小姐」選美比賽前三名。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／Miss Tiffany's Universe）"},{"pid":"df0f9947ed8e4a3d9507c34517f5a29dd97bbe63","tid":2309460,"uid":72045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T14:25:00.000Z","msg":"第3名差咁多嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aa631ba051327b844798868c77f6ebbf6630a33","tid":2309460,"uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cit